OL,3,CLucky escape for woman injured by
OL,4,Cmetal pole through windscreen
OL,6,FFiona Saunders told ITV News
OL,7,FMeridian's Lucy Warhurst she's still
OL,8,Fgetting vivid flashbacks two weeks
OL,9,Fafter the traumatising incident.
OL,11,FA Hampshire mum who was injured when a
OL,12,Flarge metal pole crashed through her
OL,13,Fcar windscreen, is calling on drivers
OL,14,Fto take care when tying down loads.
OL,16,FFiona Saunders from Cowplain was
OL,17,Fdriving along Portsdown Hill Road on
OL,18,F18 December when an unsecured pole
OL,19,Fcame off another vehicle and impaled
OL,20,Fher car.
