OL,3,CLucky escape for woman injured by
OL,4,Cmetal pole through windscreen
OL,6,FMrs Saunders said: "The next thing
OL,7,Fthere was just noise and pain. I was
OL,8,Fsat in the car, covered in glass with
OL,9,Fthis great big pole sat next to me."
OL,11,F"I originally thought it had come
OL,12,Fthrough the centre of the windscreen
OL,13,Fbut it actually came through the
OL,14,Fdriver side of the windscreen but at
OL,15,Fan angle."
OL,17,F"It took my left hand off the steering
OL,18,Fwheel and went into the passenger
OL,19,Fseat."
