OL,4,Cmetal pole through windscreen
OL,6,FThe incident left her with a severe
OL,7,Farm injury, which was down to the
OL,8,Fbone. She will need physiotherapy to
OL,9,Fhelp regain the strength in her arm,
OL,10,Fhowever Mrs Saunders says it could
OL,11,Fhave been much worse.
OL,13,FShe said: "I am so lucky, there's no
OL,14,Fdenying that, I am so lucky."
OL,16,F"A couple more inches the wrong way
OL,17,Fand it would have been a different
OL,18,Fstory. Or if I'd have had a passenger
OL,19,For my children in the car, it doesn't
OL,20,Fbear thinking about."
