OL,4,Cmetal pole through windscreen
OL,6,FMrs Saunders says the other driver did
OL,7,Fnot stop, but believes they may not
OL,8,Fhave been aware of what happened.
OL,10,FShe says she would like them to be
OL,11,Fidentified in order for them to take
OL,12,Ffinancial responsibility and realise
OL,13,Fthe consequences of having an
OL,14,Funsecured load.
OL,16,F"It's not worth taking the risk of not
OL,17,Fchecking, double checking, triple
OL,18,Fchecking that everything is as secure
OL,19,Fas it possibly can be."
