OL,6,FFiona has thanked the emergency
OL,7,Fservices, along with the off-duty
OL,8,Fparamedic and patient transport driver
OL,9,Fwho stopped to help her.
OL,11,FShe said: "I was very very, fortunate.
OL,12,FThe Police arrived really quickly and
OL,13,Fthen the ambulance crew afterwards and
OL,14,FI just couldn't be more thankful for
OL,15,Ftheir hard work and support."
OL,17,FTwo weeks on, she says she is still
OL,18,Fsuffering vivid flashbacks. She hopes
OL,19,Fthat in sharing her story, she will
OL,20,Fhelp prevent it happening to someone
OL,21,Felse.
